      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 20:09:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>丰业银行因两位分析师兄弟退出而放弃对 37 只股票的评级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/scotia-drops-coverage-of-37-stocks-as-two-analyst-brothers-exit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，由于两名担任股票分析师的兄弟退出加拿大丰业银行，该银行一天之内就取消了对 37 只股票的研究覆盖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/scotia-drops-coverage-of-37-stocks-as-two-analyst-brothers-exit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 19:47:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国银行称，更高的息票支付额使信贷需求保持高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/higher-coupon-payments-keeping-demand-for-credit-high-bofa-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行策略师表示，公司债券投资者发现，自 2022 年以来利率不断上升后，他们的利息收入正在大幅增加，而且随着他们将这些资金重新投资于投资级信贷市场，估值可以保持相对较高的水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/higher-coupon-payments-keeping-demand-for-credit-high-bofa-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 19:47:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>史蒂夫·沃兹尼亚克对苹果新 AI 工具的反应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-10/steve-wozniak-reacts-to-apple-s-new-ai-tools-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果联合创始人史蒂夫·沃兹尼亚克对苹果在公司年度全球开发者大会上宣布的备受期待的全新人工智能功能做出了反应。在接受 Alix Steel 和 Romaine Bostick 的“彭博市场：收盘”节目采访时，沃兹尼亚克表示他对“Apple Intelligence”非常感兴趣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-10/steve-wozniak-reacts-to-apple-s-new-ai-tools-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 19:41:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储会议纪要：股市小幅上涨，欧元下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/euro-falls-after-elections-us-stock-futures-steady-market-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在投资者谨慎观望美联储决议和关键通胀数据之际，股市勉强上涨。苹果公司在发布新的人工智能功能后股价仍下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/euro-falls-after-elections-us-stock-futures-steady-market-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 22:27:15 GMT</pubDate>
